    <!--Main Content start-->
    <div class="banner" id="lifeatholtec">
        <h1>Life at Holtec Asia</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="about-section">
        <div class="about-header">
            <h2>When we innovate and collaborate, it creates invaluable possibilities for everyone.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stats">
            <div class="stat-item">
                <img src="../Images/employees.png" alt="Employees">
                <h3>20,000+</h3>
                <p>Holtec Asia employees unlocking their potential</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <img src="../Images/global.png" alt="Global Offices">
                <h3>50+</h3>
                <p>Global offices strengthening our inclusive culture</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <img src="../Images/business&Collaboration.png" alt="Business Units">
                <h3>10</h3>
                <p>Business units driving collaboration</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="benefits-section">
            <h2>Live well from day 1: Benefits at Holtec Asia</h2>
            <p>We are committed to supporting the health and wellbeing of our diverse workforce across the globe.</p>
            <p>As part of that commitment, Holtec Asia offers generous benefit programs and policies that are designed using global standards to ensure the financial, emotional, social, and physical wellbeing of all our employees and their loved ones.</p>
            <form asp-action="Alljobs">
            <button>Apply now</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="why-join-section" id="why-join-section">
        <h2>Why join Holtec Asia?</h2>
        <div class="benefits-container">
            <div class="benefit-item">
                <img src="../Images/career&development.jpg" alt="Learning and Development">
                <h3>Learning and career development</h3>
                <p>Feed your curiosity through industry-leading content from Holtec Asia's Learning Academies and open new doors. Your opportunity network to make impact and form mentorships.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item">
                <img src="../Images/efforts.jpg_large" alt="Inclusion Efforts">
                <h3>Our inclusion efforts</h3>
                <p>We strive to create a culture of decency and belonging at Holtec Asia. Our action plans and key initiatives deepen our culture of inclusion and drive equitable access to opportunities.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item">
                <img src="../Images/forceofgood.webp" alt="Force of Good">
                <h3>Be a force of good</h3>
                <p>At Holtec Asia, we believe in doing well by doing good. We are on a mission to build a sustainable world that unlocks invaluable possibilities for all.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!--Main Content end-->
